.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大約100-400水深就搵到 唔難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24f83ea9a6d507d6245b66b25bc641191abf6d7","tid":917784,"uid":73412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"我都係，3年前係東京食過一次真係好撚好食，跟住呢幾年我完全搵唔到邊度相似既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ab3cabae20e510ff59df9772ca72901da63c09","tid":917784,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b179eac47e6bb09199bde5f1eeb35a95228998","tid":917784,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港連鎖店返貨返得閪啫，靚既赤身都有鋪頭返既"},{"pid":"3371db29acf99ae633b0ab355ed81e8a4ac5dfff","tid":917784,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef2eb084bd47f1a51689d5278c14a712900a0f8","tid":917784,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"質素問題啫"},{"pid":"2bcd84978d5a35396ae40f3d4f4d6857d2fccec5","tid":917784,"uid":200781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"唔係魚嘅問題 係同邊個食嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4e4d93e56763ecab9bf93024b6456acc85553d","tid":917784,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:08:30.000Z","msg":"貴果d咪好食囉"},{"pid":"6081270ddab8db86737d50640c0fb9e08fcf6bb3","tid":917784,"uid":26106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"全部大吞都會好味嫁啦<br />\n赤身就真係冇咩邊間好食"},{"pid":"c1435b9d359b038676274d088a9771d00428c7e6","tid":917784,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"去sogo壽司攤檔有啲寫住鮪魚揀嗰啲黎買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03e592d5930b3c9286d6cc9737063de90314db9","tid":917784,"uid":191510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"係咪吞拿魚腩<br />\n真係好好食<br />\n不過幾貴"},{"pid":"ff67aa3ac167d2ad12eb40c4aed45fa1f836dd38","tid":917784,"uid":19979,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"樓主在數年前與朋友一同遭遇海難，在海上漂流了一陣子，甚至差點餓死。在最危急的時候朋友做了吞拿魚刺身給樓主，欺騙樓主吞拿魚是從海中獵獲的。<br />\n<br />\n這救了樓主一命的吞拿魚刺身，美好的滋味讓他永遠無法忘懷，獲救後的某天得知這家餐館裡有提供吞拿魚刺身，便決定前來回味吞拿魚的味道。<br />\n<br />\n然而，吃了幾口後卻發現口中的刺身與記憶中的味道完全不同，就在此時才意識到一件事：原來遇難時所吃的吞拿魚刺身，其實是他那後來衰弱而死的朋友，當時為了讓樓主有機會活命下去而取自己身上的肉供樓主食用。<br />\n<br />\n由於樓主是位盲人，當時並不清楚朋友聲稱的吞拿魚刺身是否真的是捕獲而來，一直到這時候才意識到這件事的樓主，便因為打擊過大而跳崖自殺了。"},{"pid":"d6f7e292d830b6bf0d45ccaffb876ffb6afcc0f9","tid":917784,"uid":43839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af445d61f05112db56b5179d0e024518edf950af","tid":917784,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"之後就一直食唔番嗰種味，之後次次食日本野我都會叫少少吞拿魚刺身，但次次食完都有種好難食嘅感覺，不如都係食番三文魚算數，但個朋友已經無聯絡，所以可能永遠食唔番嗰種味，如果吞拿魚咁好味我真係可以唔再食三文魚，我想問邊度食吞拿魚好味架？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"首先你果隻吞拿魚係咩色?<br />\n<br />\n白色?鮮紅色?暗紅色?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww8amTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww8amTN.jpg&h=a95491e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuRLaNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuRLaNa.jpg&h=f21b4ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcJEZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcJEZFL.jpg&h=be552b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6STxAd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6STxAd9.jpg&h=2303c6c0&s={SIZE}\" 